what: American Community Survey population data — acs
title: American Community Survey population data — acs
text: data sets contain population data Kansas City, Missouri, sourced US Census Bureau's American Community Survey (ACS). 1-year ACS data sets, summary level Kansas City . 5-year ACS data sets, summary levels include city, county, census tract, census block group, ZIP code tabulation area (ZCTA). Data sets downloaded data.census.gov using tidycensus package. data variables full collapsed Age Sex, Race, Hispanic Origin tables included (.e., tables beginning B01, B02, B03, C01, C02, C03). See Guidance Data Users information use ACS data.
